{"tid":1638530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[告黨鐵] 所有買過全月通既巴絲入","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:27:29.000Z","uid":264202,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c90d0d1bc9093427a852703a03890d2c36fe414b","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"作為專業港豬，每日仲搭黨鐵仲見到佢個垃圾口號就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢自己閂埋真係好嬲，話收幾點就幾點有冇搞錯！<br />\n<br />\n而家我就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去消委會告9黨鐵！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 去消委會投訴表格</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/cc-complaint/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumer.org.hk%2Fws_chi%2Fcc-complaint%2Findex.php&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=94251a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/cc-complaint/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 填寫好資料，個人地址求其都填都得</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/cc-complaint/index.php\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumer.org.hk%2Fws_chi%2Fcc-complaint%2Findex.php&h=57db11b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 黨鐵地址一定係填返垃圾九龍灣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九龍灣，偉業街33號，德福廣場港鐵總部大樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 投訴揀<strong>服務</strong><br />\n行業係<strong>公共交通</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 投訴個案撮要</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我購買了十月的全月通，但港鐵停駛並無法於預期內通知未來行車狀況。<br />\n<br />\n第一，我購買的&ldquo;全月通&ldquo;理應服務範圍應有一個月，但實際可使用的日期並沒有一個月。<br />\n第二，港鐵隨意關閉特定鐵路站的原因並不合理，令我的旅程不斷延誤無法計劃行程，與港鐵的服務&ldquo;心繫生活每一程&ldquo;完全不一。<br />\n第三，港鐵可以毫無原故，沒有任何事情發生並提早停駛全部列車並不合理，導致我無法享用其服務。<br />\n<br />\n我強烈要求退款和港鐵更正以上事情做法，刻不容援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">完！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7a20a31e9796eac7c4d1691d251db2ba0448204","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c4ed29dca8353a434427efb29cf40a9cbea9983","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"c54b763d1e57517098d06cbd93b120b80dd8d211","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"快啲動手"},{"pid":"9c235d7c96257b8f252a486ca6e612a0f67aa04a","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"468936b5bcdac0874f03fdc44ca1a5f723464002","tid":1638530,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d181921c9ab8e52408b8f62f6e673029307c5af","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54ccf94fcc5b5414edc53394d9d1f65f3956a974","tid":1638530,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5be967643876c6915ac73e06712ca1b725066c","tid":1638530,"uid":264202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:49:21.000Z","msg